how Messages are being passed ?? 

Packets and Routers.

what are packets ??

as the need to send bulk messages increased, Network engineers came up with a breaking messages into smaller bit called ("PACKETS"), before sending them, these invention even made sending messages faster, unlike  during the olden days when we use store and forward method to communicate, I'm not going into what store and forward is in details, buh it's basically connecting bunch of computers together in order for us to send message, as long as one computer is connected to another, you can send message to any part of the world, buh it was not efficient cause you have to wait for like days or even months before you can recieve your message, there are alot of factors that can determine how quick you can get your message tho. but the invention of breaking down messages into smaller fragments before sending them helped in making message transfer efficient.


what are Routers ??

Routers are devices that helps to recieve and send data between computer networks.


